{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/restyle-with-stylish","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>准备工作</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://coderfe.cn/2016/04/21/high-quality-apps-windows-ios-android/\">Chrome 浏览器</a></li>\n<li>安装<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/fjnbnpbmkenffdnngjfgmeleoegfcffe\">Styleish 插件</a></li>\n<li>一丢丢<code class=\"language-text\">CSS</code>基础</li>\n</ul>\n<h2>QQ 空间优化</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>打开你的<a href=\"http://qzone.qq.com/\">QQ 空间</a>，点击<strong>右上角那个 S 字母的图标</strong>，选择<strong>编写样式给这个 URL</strong></li>\n<li>第一步完成会打开一个写代码的窗口，复制<a href=\"https://github.com/coderfe/cssstyles/blob/master/qzone-redesign.css\">我的样式</a>到那个框框里，输入名称，保存</li>\n<li>优雅地刷好友动态</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://oaz5uxplb.bkt.clouddn.com/blog/qzone-restyle.gif\" alt=\"qzone-restyle\"></p>\n<h2>微博的优化</h2>\n<ul>\n<li>有现成的微博样式供你选择<a href=\"https://userstyles.org/styles/106272/weibo-v6\">weibo_v6</a>和<a href=\"https://userstyles.org/styles/123737/weibo-v6-patch\">weibo<em>v6</em>patch</a></li>\n<li>打开<a href=\"http://www.weibo.com\">微博</a>，点击按钮，编写样式</li>\n<li>复制<a href=\"https://github.com/coderfe/cssstyles/blob/master/weibo-redesign.css\">我的样式</a>，粘贴</li>\n<li>优雅的刷微博</li>\n</ul>\n<p><img src=\"http://oaz5uxplb.bkt.clouddn.com/blog/weibo-restyle.gif\" alt=\"weibo-restyle\"></p>\n<h2>其他</h2>\n<p>如果你有兴趣可以再添加其他样式，并且 Stylish 可以实现的远不止这些，等待你的发掘！\n其次，微博的样式是在前两个样式的基础上加了一些背景图片和动画效果，感谢原作者的创作！</p>","tableOfContents":"<ul>\n<li><a href=\"/restyle-with-stylish/#%E5%87%86%E5%A4%87%E5%B7%A5%E4%BD%9C\">准备工作</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/restyle-with-stylish/#qq-%E7%A9%BA%E9%97%B4%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96\">QQ 空间优化</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/restyle-with-stylish/#%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%E7%9A%84%E4%BC%98%E5%8C%96\">微博的优化</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"/restyle-with-stylish/#%E5%85%B6%E4%BB%96\">其他</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"path":"/restyle-with-stylish","date":"Apr 23, 2016","title":"Stylish —— 优雅地刷网页","tldr":"在 PC 端 QQ 空间看朋友动态、刷微博的时候你是否觉得有些东西太碍眼、太复杂了，对，我就是这样觉的，所以呢，下面就让 Stylish 还给你一个清爽优雅的界面。","tags":["CSS"]},"timeToRead":1}},"pageContext":{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"一些我自己常用的优质Apps","path":"/my-favorite-apps"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"利用 TravisCI 自动部署 Hexo blog","path":"/automatic-deploy-hexo-blog-with-travis-ci"}},"relatedPosts":[{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 渐变的角度问题","path":"/css-gradient-angles"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"『译』在你的 WordPress 项目中使用 Let's Encrypt SSL","path":"/use-lets-encrypt-in-wordpress"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/ie8-compatibility","tags":["CSS"],"title":"IE8 兼容性总结"}}},{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 中有趣的 filter 属性","path":"/css-filter-property"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"IE8 兼容性总结","path":"/ie8-compatibility"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/css-gradient-angles","tags":["CSS"],"title":"CSS 渐变的角度问题"}}},{"next":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Gulp and Browser-sync","path":"/use-browser-sync-with-gulp"}},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"title":"CSS 渐变的角度问题","path":"/css-gradient-angles"}},"node":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/css-filter-property","tags":["CSS"],"title":"CSS 中有趣的 filter 属性"}}}]}}}